Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八幕\N布洛涅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然進來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我怎麼叫你都不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香榭麗捨的客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說今日不想見您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼口信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能賞光參觀新別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請您參加晚會的請貼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必與家人同往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奧特伊的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;12;0;90,{\a6}{\fs20}Auteuil：巴黎西部市郊的一個區，莫裏哀等作家喜愛居住的地方。周圍是布洛涅（Boulogne）森林。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼荒涼的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這是伯爵的個人意願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是屬於維爾福先生的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的女主人在時 這裏非常華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是瓦朗蒂娜的親生母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時還是年輕貌美的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是維爾福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是外子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席檢察官大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說內人與犬子承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得您賞光親臨 實在蓬蓽生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座別墅用來招待客人還稍顯冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 不知為何我特別喜歡清靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如今代表巴黎的三位紳士都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融王唐格拉爾氏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌攬軍隊實權的莫爾塞夫將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有司掌法律的您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日招待各位參加這個簡陋的聚會不為別樁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我向大家坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅者是不安之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能和三位建立友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍閣下是否渴望大統領的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從何處聽聞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請讓我略盡綿薄之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 你先離席一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人之間有話要談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 呆坐著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒事 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬拉你過來 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵…是不是在避開我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在維爾福先生家看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…伯爵和夫人有染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候伯爵發現了我在偷窺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵也有不為人知的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不是為了馬克西米利安的事而去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是另外一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與二位相伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吹吹夜風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在…在下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安·莫雷爾大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是位傑出的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下獵犬座γ方面軍陸軍上尉 馬克西米利安·莫雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家在馬賽從事貿易 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在下和令嬡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從事著保衛國家的高尚工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我對表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您只是一介平民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而小女已有未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 望您諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是越洋而來的馬賽風味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…她對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼悄悄話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然突然對首席檢察官按下快門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠膽大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到囂張的傢伙就叛逆心理作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 青春的煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 這世上一個二個都為情所困
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 以前那兩人也傳過緋聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首席檢察官和歐仁妮的母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不情之請 實在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鋼琴課也花了不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在這種時候露兩手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽我說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向您道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我…未考慮您的想法就出言不遜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩事都丟給你了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐仁妮那傢伙彈得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被她騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會兒跟她聊過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是我說壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還來找我幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看見怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在這裏…把那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂就如您的天職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天職嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵認識很多有才能的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您出色的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的人兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為展示年輕人們的才華橫溢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我再引薦一位年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亞·卡瓦爾坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家族還有繼承人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父親是我的舊友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若大家能像待我一樣待他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不勝榮幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是剛繼承亡父領地的後生晚輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他的胸飾 看樣子值500萬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的新寵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能非常有才華哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 抱歉打斷各位暢談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能承蒙稍微側目一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買下這座別墅是為了遠離城市喧囂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過清靜離群的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說來也奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際來到這裏的我迷上了這幢古宅的某種氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該如何形容呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁去想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前這座別墅裏人們過著怎樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是隱藏了怎樣不為人知的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次想起 我都充滿著無以言表的喜悅和平穩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊 說什麼詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官大人察覺不到這座宅子裏陰鬱邪惡的氣氛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席檢察官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼由您親自來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在這座宅子裏只留有一間未使用的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房間被認為是這邪惡氣氛瀰漫的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 不要這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就遵從一下主人的意願嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來參觀一下這間邪惡的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去的話 也無甚興味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有歐仁妮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成三組去尋找那間房 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓三個年輕人先行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗宅邸至深之處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將贈予平安到達的人一份薄禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生 拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 侯爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您氣色不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請認真一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先發方能制人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一問 侯爵出身何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我來自銀河東方的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一片非常美麗的行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中某顆星上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種吸取礦石菁華 孕育寶石之卵的鳥類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年1次為繁殖而築巢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能和您單獨交談了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我想和您談談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 莫爾塞夫夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡氣氛的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為何對馬賽如此介懷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話怎講
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的菜餚也安排了馬賽口味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是看到您就想起以前認識的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長久以來 我都只為再見他一面而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在不知為何卻感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是孤獨一人 絕不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直想念著您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘了那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是亡父給我的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到盡頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧 阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否感到愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這座別墅奇異的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這宅邸的主人看來不知何為待客之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我一個小忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您如此幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了 在維爾福先生家的溫室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 您看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人太熱情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為您一定非常生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 應該由我說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也無法與您暢談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我在遠方宇宙得了一種病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會不見任何人來修養
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾會感到麻痹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 這是只屬於你和我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我會保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拿著這個盒子出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…那孩子出生的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…是那孩子把我們引來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是17年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是伯爵送的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準戀人們的毒針
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毒手也會降臨到自己頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九幕\N夢見黑暗之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待

